      • VObjectLS

        public VObjectLS(byte[] bytes,
                 int offset,
                 int length)
          throws KlvParseException
        Create the local set from encoded bytes.

        This is the parser logic for the VObject Local Set to extract the message from part of a byte array.

        Parameters:
        bytes - Encoded bytes
        offset - the offset into the bytes array to start parsing
        length - the number of bytes to parse
        Throws:
        KlvParseException - if the bytes could not be parsed.
